Package: kbfix
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1, python3-pynput, python3-pyperclip
Description: KBFix - convert selected text RU/EN using hotkey, no system layout changes
 KBFix is a desktop utility for Linux that converts selected text between RU and EN via hotkey.
 It does not change the system keyboard layout and works via clipboard.
